This example is of RecyclerView with different items in the Adapter.

Files
    - RecyclerViewExample2.java:
        Main Activity java file.
    - activity_recycler_view_example2.xml:
        Layout xml file of Activity.
    - item_text_image.xml:
        Layout xml file of item with image and text.
    - item_text_only.xml:
        Layout xml file of item with only text.
